text: Borhan Uddin Ahmed is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Jessore-2. ==Career== Ahmed was elected to parliament from Jessore-2 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. He was a leader of Sarbadaliya Chhatra Sangram Parishad. He is the Chairman of Doreen Group. He is the convener of Former Chatra League Members Foundation. He was previously the president of the foundation. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
